article.headline: Gardner-Webb 73, Stetson 48
article.story: BOILING SPRINGS, N.C. (AP) -- Takayo Siddle scored a career-high 17 points as Gardner-Webb rolled to a 73-48 Atlantic Sun Conference victory Saturday night over Stetson. Chris Gash had five 3-pointers for the Bulldogs (9-17, 7-8). Grayson Flittner and Ricky McPhee had 10 each. Matt French grabbed nine rebounds and scored nine points. Garfield Blair scored nine points to lead Stetson (8-17, 4-10), which hit six of 28 shots in the second half.
